OL,3,CNorth East pothole repairs backlog
OL,4,Cwill cost #820m, says new survey
OL,6,FOur reporter Kris Jepson has been in
OL,7,FDarlington, speaking to people in the
OL,8,Ftown who have had to repair their cars
OL,9,Fdue to pot holes.
OL,11,FA new survey has suggested it will
OL,12,Fcost #821.1 million to tackle the
OL,13,Fbacklog of carriageway road repairs in
OL,14,Fthe North East and bring the network
OL,15,Fup to standard, to enable it to be
OL,16,Fmaintained efficiently and in a cost
OL,17,Feffective way going forward.
