OL,3,CNorth East pothole repairs backlog
OL,4,Cwill cost #820m, says new survey
OL,6,FThe ALARM (Annual Local Authority Road
OL,7,FMaintenance) survey, published 19
OL,8,FMarch 2024, said on 33 per cent of
OL,9,Flocal roads in the region are in a
OL,10,F"good structural condition", while the
OL,11,Fremaining 6,640 miles of road (67 per
OL,12,Fcent) will most likely need rebuilding
OL,13,Fin the next 15 years if they continue
OL,14,Fto deteriorate without appropriate
OL,15,Fmaintenance measures.
