OL,3,CNorth East pothole repairs backlog
OL,4,Cwill cost #820m, says new survey
OL,6,FDavid Giles from The Asphalt Industry
OL,7,FAlliance, the group who conducted the
OL,8,Fsurvey, told ITV News Tyne Tees: "The
OL,9,Flife that's left it two thirds of the
OL,10,Froads is 15 years and yes, you'd
OL,11,Feither have to reconstruct the roads
OL,12,For, at the very least, take off a
OL,13,Flayer and resurface the roads.
OL,15,F"Local authorities haven't been given
OL,16,Fthe money they need to keep the roads
OL,17,Fin the condition that we all need as a
OL,18,Fsociety."
