OL,3,CNorth East pothole repairs backlog
OL,4,Cwill cost #820m, says new survey
OL,6,FPrime Minister, Rishi Sunak, visited
OL,7,FDarlington in March 2023 and declared
OL,8,Fnew spending to help repair potholes
OL,9,Fin the country.
OL,11,FThe survey suggested #15.2 million has
OL,12,Fbeen spent filling in 211,008 potholes
OL,13,Fover the last 12 months in the North
OL,14,FEast, as a result, but that
OL,15,Fcarriageway maintenance budgets are 14
OL,16,Fper cent lower in the region, compared
OL,17,Fto the average for England (excluding
OL,18,FLondon) at #16.0 million per authority
OL,19,F(England: #18.7 million).
