OL,6,FDrivers in Darlington were united in
OL,7,Ftheir frustrations with potholes in
OL,8,Fthe area when approached by ITV News.
OL,10,FOne driver said: "Well, if we're going
OL,11,Fto be paying for something, they
OL,12,Fshould be fixed properly at least.
OL,14,F"I don't know whether it's the quality
OL,15,Fof what they're fixing it with, if
OL,16,Fit's a cheap solution or something,
OL,17,Fbut something needs to be done about
OL,18,Fit, you know. I cant afford to keep
OL,19,Ffixing my car. I've literally just had
OL,20,Fto get two new tyres. Popped wheel."
