OL,6,FAnother Darlington based woman added:
OL,7,F"Very expensive to fix I guess, when
OL,8,Fyou don't spot them and, well, I
OL,9,Fshould know. I've had to get my breaks
OL,10,Fand stuff fixed before, so yeh, very
OL,11,Fannoying."
